text: Abdur Jamal is a masculine Muslim name. Abdur Jamal, Abdul Jamal, or variants may refer to: * Abdul Jamal Shah of Pahang (died 1575), the Sultan of Pahang, Malaysia * Temenggong Abdul Jamal (1720–1802), the first Temenggong of Johor, Malaysia ==See also== * Abdul Jalal, chief of police, Kunar Province, Afghanistan * Abdul Jamil, a Muslim given name of Arabic origin
title: Abdul Jamal
